genresAdvancedInfo.name: fnf
genresAdvancedInfo.description: "fnf" is a music genre that originated from the popular music rhythm game, Friday Night Funkin'. It features upbeat electronic beats, catchy melodies, and clever lyrics that are perfect for dancing and singing along to. The genre is characterized by its use of retro video game sounds and funky grooves that will keep you moving all night long.
